Object.assign(translations.en.articleBodies, {
      "edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended": [
            "[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/01.png|Open-Ended editing screen]]\n\nAfter clicking **+ Manual**, select **Quiz → Open-Ended** in the **Create Manually** popup to add the Activity.\n\nIn the center of the slide, the question title, subtitle, and the text box where students enter their responses are displayed. In preview, a sample answer appears inside the text box.\n\n### Setting options (right panel)\n\n**Background Color**\n\n- Freely change the slide background color in the color picker. You can also enter a Hex code directly.\n\n**Common Setting**\n\n- **1 Second's Countdown**: Turn on the toggle to run a 1-second countdown before the question appears.\n\n**Time Limit**\n\n- Turn on the toggle to set a time limit for submitting responses. When it is off, the activity runs without a time limit.",
            "[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/02.png|Open-Ended class start screen]]\n\nOn the class screen, the question title, subtitle, and related image are displayed in the center. The **Write the correct answer.** button appears at the bottom, and the teacher can click it to enter a model answer in advance.\n\nClick **Let's Begin** to start student responses. While students submit responses, click **Instructor View** in the upper right to check submission status (Submitted / Not Submitted).\n\n[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/04.png|Open-Ended model answer reveal screen]]\n\nWhen response collection is complete, click **Finish Up**. The model answer entered by the teacher is then revealed on screen in the form **The correct answer is**. After that, click **View Result** to move to the student response result screen.",
            "[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/05.png|Open-Ended student screen before input]]\n\nOn the student screen, the question title, subtitle, and related image are displayed. On the left, the **Enter Answer** input box appears, and on the right, the **Write your Answer** label and **Submit** button appear.\n\n[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/06.png|Student entering an Open-Ended response]]\n\nThe student taps the text box and freely enters their response. When input is complete, the **Submit** button becomes active in blue and can be used to submit.\n\n[[image:edit-lesson-quiz-open-ended/08.png|Open-Ended submission complete screen]]\n\nAfter submission, the screen shows the **Your answer is** message together with the student's written response, and a character animation indicates that submission is complete."
      ]
});
