                          "[[image:toolkit-wheel/01.png|Wheel choice count setting screen]]\n\nOn the first screen, use the **− / +** buttons to set the number of wheel choices. You can set up to **8 choices** (\"You can set up to 8 choices\"). After setting the number, click **Set**.\n\nThe number of wheel choices means the number of selection areas shown at once. Set the required number first based on the number of student names or items.",
