                          "title": "9. Quick Poll",
                          "desc": "Quick Poll is a tool for asking a simple question during class and counting student responses on the spot. You can directly record response counts with the − / + buttons for each option, and it supports four formats.",
                          "note": "Click the tool icon in Tool Kit at the bottom of the class screen to run it.",
