                          "[[image:toolkit-first-to-buzz/01.png|First to Buzz ready screen]]\n\nWhen it first opens, the **Get ready!** screen is displayed. The screen shows a large button image along with the notice **Press the button only once. The faster you press, the higher your rank.**\n\nStudents should press the button only once, and the faster they press, the higher their rank becomes. After checking the notice, the teacher clicks **Start** to begin participation.",
